        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about__description">
        <h2>Hello</h2>
        <p class="about__intro">Here is who I am & what I do</p>
        <div class="about__nav">
          <button class="button button-primary">Resume</button>
          <button class="button button-secondary">Projects</button>
        </div>
        <p class="about_bio">
          I am Jimmy Álvarez, a web developer from San José, Costa Rica, with
          experience as a Senior Web Developer at Accenture. I am passionate
          about programming, automation, and improving productivity. With an
          analytical and problem-solving mindset, I enjoy tackling challenges
          and optimizing repetitive tasks.
          <br /> <br>
          My career in technology began with studies in Programming and Web Design
          at CETAV. In addition to programming, I value teamwork and continuous learning.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
